{
  "stem": "15017.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Before I left school, I won my first scholarship, then I won a year's free tuition at the Royal Academy-- another scholarship and the violin was given to me-- and I won a year's free tuition at the Royal Academy of Music.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In London.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything was in London.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, I got a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was playing in a cinema during the silence.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everything was going--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1920-- November 1925.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I left school in April 1925, and I got my first job.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was earning very good money, you see?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went on until the talkies started to come in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I saw that, in spite of what everybody was saying, this was another thing that was happening.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The people would say, the musicians that used to be from Archer Street [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It'll never work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's canned music, and all that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father, you see, is a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when I had a moment, I always had to go up into the workshop, pulling bastings and things like that, and learning how to sew.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I think I showed you the other day the thimble that I had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When my father put that thimble on my finger, I had to walk around the workshop with my finger like that, showing everybody that the [NON-ENGLISH], you see.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyhow, my father wanted me to go into the workshop.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I said, uh-uh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He wanted me to be a [NON-ENGLISH], and I said, I don't want-- he says, if you don't want to be a [NON-ENGLISH], you'd better find yourself a job quickly.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I went to the West End, which is the-- like, the downtown of-- of-- of London, the West End.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I gave an audition.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I had no money in my pocket.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
